{"event": "USER_RESPONSE", "message": "What is the most critical open decision right now and which agent owns it?", "response_text": "## Most Critical Open Decision\n\n**Agent:** `[a2]` \u2014 audit and harden REST API authentication/authorisation\n\n**Decision:** How to securely store JWT access tokens (currently in `localStorage`, which is vulnerable to XSS attacks)\n\n**Why it's most critical:**\n- It's a **security vulnerability** (vs. a3's latency issue, which is performance)\n- A compromised token grants full user account access\n- Affects the entire platform's trust model\n\n**Agent [a3]** also has HIGH urgency, but p99 latency at 1s is a degradation issue rather than an exposure risk. Security issues take precedence.", "ts": "2026-04-05T19:27:26.535Z"}
